        <rule name="Halberd-Gun" id="4e0a-4177-04c9-3da9" hidden="false">
          <description>Enemies charging a model equipped with a Halberd-gun add -1 DICE in melee combat when rolling to hit. This only applies when a model attacks after a charge, not on subsequent rounds of melee</description>
