        <profile name="Mastery of the Elements" typeId="86ac-f459-ca64-1e52" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="c059-cb25-b9d4-19d9">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="896f-6fa6-64e7-5801">At the beginning of a battle, all ranged and melee weapons that an Alchemist has been equipped with may be assigned one of the following Keywords: SHRAPNEL, FIRE or GAS added to them. All the weapons the Alchemist has will share the same Keyword. With a RISKY ACTION with +1 DICE, the Alchemist can change this Keyword into one of the others.</characteristic>
